==车站概要==
本站位于三友路与二环路北四段交叉口，沿二环路北四段呈西北、东南向布置，于2016年7月31日启用<ref name="启用">{{cite news  | title = 成都地铁3号线一期工程试运营 熊猫主题列车首发  | publisher = 新浪  | date = 2016-07-31  | url = http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2016-07-31/doc-ifxunuyk4220798.shtml  | accessdate = 2016-07-31  | language = zh  | archive-date = 2016-08-01  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160801212833/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2016-07-31/doc-ifxunuyk4220798.shtml  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>。因位于[[成华区|成华区]][[府青路街道|府青路街道]]李家沱社区而得名。3号线一期原规划并无此站，后因市民呼声，而增设<ref>{{cite news  | title = 地铁3号线新方案增加磨子桥和李家沱站  | publisher = 新浪  | date = 2014-06-16  | url = http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2014-06-16/045030367185.shtml  | accessdate = 2014-06-16  | language = zh  | archive-date = 2017-08-31  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170831132139/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2014-06-16/045030367185.shtml  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>。在建设期间是成都地铁3号线一期工程的装修样板车站<ref>{{cite news | title = 川网探访地铁3号线“样板间”李家沱站 有面子更有里子(组图) | publisher = 网易 | date = 2015-11-26 | url = http://news.163.com/15/1126/19/B9CDD5P200014AEE.html | accessdate = 2015-11-26 | language = zh | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171210071700/http://news.163.com/15/1126/19/B9CDD5P200014AEE.html | archive-date = 2017-12-10 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

